Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OVA第一話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WATER·WAR！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰的賽場在南方的小島上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然開場說了一句“所以呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定俗成的吐槽真像小桃桃的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我小桃桃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 難得有海灘 大家不如下水游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是個好點子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..沒有泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有學校指定的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去買吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百貨公司裏面有很棒的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！大家一起去買泳衣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是和泳衣沾邊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣一應俱全就是這家店的賣點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從古至今？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無奇不有？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 所有種類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再現了龐貝壁畫的最古老的兩件式泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19世紀的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜聞樂見的條紋泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古今東西的電影明星穿著的時尚名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連封面女郎穿著的泳裝也可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢幻的吸睛泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人..穿這個會受歡迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂講啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個看起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶嗡~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是淑女們最愛的花紋泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這件是走少女風格的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力無法擋啊 果然要這樣才對嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥特風的泳衣 一直很想穿穿看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這款是帶有佩斯利花紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上這件我就是風韻熟女了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起這些..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得今年的主流會是戰車風哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是戰車！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳指的是豹紋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.46,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,660)}Panther
